</style></div><div class="r-19uaj3d" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="f87d37e7-3ea2-47a8-b9b9-a426df4c020b" class="r-9jpuou"><div data-rid="3afd5c4b-c643-4040-97d7-8399e63b839b" class="r-q1mqnx"><picture data-rid="4f15dbb1-3469-4817-8915-fd1b8c3f8c3c" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-zkr9i5"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Blume_logo.png?v=1641676662&amp;width=200" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Blume_logo.png?v=1641676662&amp;width=200" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Blume_logo.png?v=1641676662&amp;width=200" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Blume_logo.png?v=1641676662" alt="The word &#x27;BLUME&#x27; written in bold blue letters." class="r-1jxkl0u" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div></div><div data-rid="364978db-77db-4cb3-bb9a-2eacdbd052e1" class="r-1eu4owh"><div data-rid="612d298a-39ac-4387-b4c5-902a014d85c4" class="r-n0lspb"><div data-rid="94c700ed-d568-4a55-a4d5-bc5b93c46e79" class="r-3rrhmu"><div data-rid="ba110f92-ee6b-41b5-87b5-36dff7f1a460" class="r-100mhjn"><div data-rid="748922af-1235-487a-8b63-ee3d30648023" class="r-1wfuqgu"><div data-rid="80c7ba8e-0a36-4662-971e-a23bf89d4760" class="r-17trofv"><div data-rid="a273b79e-964c-4d43-81e6-dd890f295fa9" class="r-1y1j4pg"><div data-rid="3cf304bb-da17-4897-af5f-d692a12d7b4a" class="r-1qo6dyb"><div data-rid="c2ef1912-f62a-45b5-9bf3-e759bfca837a" class="r-11qiwlq"><div data-rid="d563cec3-bc9d-4fd2-b6b4-cdf43f9e8755" class="r-pnr35i"><div data-rid="8ef36ab9-2ec7-4630-8a9a-fa140baad533" class="r-edrvma alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2><strong>5 Reasons Why Blume Will Clear Years of Hormonal Acne—In Just 3 Days</strong></h2></span></div><div data-rid="b620cc69-a168-4ba9-95ab-f5a2c8695b04" class="r-1m6k353 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Hormonal acne isn’t just a phase—it’s painful, unpredictable, and feels like it will never go away.</p><br><p>Maybe it shows up every month like clockwork. Maybe it’s taken over your jawline, cheeks, or forehead. Maybe your skin is extra sensitive—and every product you’ve tried either does nothing or leaves it dry, red, and breaking out even more.<br></p><br><p>You’re not alone.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume’s Clear Skin Kit was made for skin just like yours: sensitive, breakout-prone, and exhausted from years of trial and error. It’s powered by clean, proven ingredients that treat hormonal acne at the source—without the harsh side effects.<br></p><br><p>Whether you're a girl or a boy, 11, 18, in your 30s or 50+, this routine was designed to work across all life stages and skin types. And for many customers? It starts making a visible difference in just 3 days.<br></p><br><p>Here’s why Blume works when nothing else has:</p></span></div><picture data-rid="3d012ec6-7b82-4af5-9e4a-0c5c2ac34e42" class="r-fr4ta"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/bday-sale-1hm.jpg?v=1749508904#&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/bday-sale-1hm.jpg?v=1749508904#&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/bday-sale-1hm.jpg?v=1749508904#&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/bday-sale-1hm.jpg?v=1749508904#" class="r-78gxt2" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="ecc9ab24-b634-4017-83b6-ff722d9b5401" class="r-uvi5en"><div data-rid="a7ef27b2-0e10-44bd-b054-ca911bd39920" class="r-1mgdar2"><div data-rid="1e678fff-e2bf-407f-ad17-c5b8433b070a" class="r-1ihzic6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>1.  This Oil Treats Hormonal Acne at the Root—And It’s Clinically Proven</h3></span></div><div data-rid="9dbc5984-2fc2-4c8b-9f3d-0f23f6588299" class="r-1h6ghn5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most acne products sit on the surface of your skin, drying out pimples without addressing what’s causing them. Blume’s Clear Skin Kit is different.</p><br><p>It’s powered by a proprietary blend of non-comedogenic oils, including a high concentration (25%) of black cumin seed oil—one of the only natural ingredients clinically proven to fight hormonal acne below the surface.</p><br><p>Because it’s an oil, it doesn’t just sit on top—it absorbs deep into the skin, where hormonal breakouts begin, and helps flatten acne before it ever reaches the surface.</p><br><p>🔬 The secret?  Thymoquinone, the bioactive compound in black cumin seed oil.</p><ol><li><p>In clinical studies, black cumin seed oil reduced inflammatory acne lesions by up to 78% in just 8 weeks—with results equal to benzoyl peroxide, but without the irritation or dryness.</p></li><li><br></li><li><p>Thymoquinone is anti-inflammatory, antibacterial, and sebum-regulating—a triple threat for hormonal acne.</p></li><li><br></li><li><p>It’s also been shown to inhibit the growth of Cutibacterium acnes, the bacteria deeply involved in acne development.</p></li></ol><br><p>🌿 Here’s how it works:</p><ol><li><p>Antibacterial: Kills breakout-causing bacteria deep in your pores—without harsh chemicals or antibiotics.</p></li><li><br></li><li><p>Anti-inflammatory: Calms the hormone-triggered redness, swelling, and pain you feel under the skin.</p></li><li><br></li><li><p>Sebum-regulating: Balances oil production to prevent both clogged pores and dry, flaky skin.</p></li></ol><br><p>And unlike traditional acne treatments that can damage your barrier or cause rebound breakouts, black cumin seed oil is non-comedogenic, hydrating, and safe for daily use—even on sensitive skin.</p><br><p>You’re not just treating what’s visible. You’re preventing what’s coming next.<br></p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="7907e6e2-15c1-4380-8b84-ea0cf9ea6d66" class="r-j07vs4"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65" alt="Collage of facial skin progress over time with acne improvement." class="r-1tpa37o" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="860a71c8-4f31-4a46-9d42-4048c870e15a" class="r-smvqt0"><div data-rid="d01eded0-0dca-4524-9996-55d16d48e935" class="r-128nt4w"><div data-rid="2cb15daa-281d-4ea0-8c27-d35aa66f9861" class="r-i9u43n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2.  A Clinically Backed Routine That Rebuilds Your Skin While It Clears It</p></span></div><div data-rid="21c196a6-dc85-47fa-be18-9e91c89c0f12" class="r-fyxkqz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most acne products are too aggressive. They kill bacteria, but they also strip your skin—damaging your moisture barrier and leaving you with more breakouts, irritation, and redness than when you started.</p><br><p>Blume’s Clear Skin Kit does the opposite. It’s a 3-step routine made to treat breakouts while actively repairing and strengthening your skin barrier—so you’re not just clearing your skin, you’re restoring it.</p><br><p>Each ingredient was carefully chosen to heal, hydrate, and protect acne-prone skin:</p><p>🧪 Ceramides: Naturally occurring lipids that:</p><ul><li><p>Rebuild your skin barrier and shield it from irritation and pollution</p></li><li><p>Are clinically proven to reduce inflammation and sensitivity in acne-prone skin</p></li><li><p>Lock in moisture—essential for preventing future breakout</p></li></ul><p>🧪 Squalane: A lightweight, non-comedogenic hydrator that:</p><ul><li><p>Mimics your skin’s natural oils for deep, breathable moisture</p></li><li><p>Calms redness and supports long-term barrier repair</p></li><li><p>Boosts elasticity and keeps your skin smooth, balanced, and resilient</p></li></ul><p>🧪 Glycerin: A plant-derived humectant clinically shown to:</p><ul><li><p>Increase skin hydration by up to 35% in just 7 days</p></li><li><p>Maintain moisture balance to prevent overproduction of oil</p></li><li><p>Soften dry, reactive skin while visibly improving texture and tone</p></li></ul><br><p>Glycerin draws moisture into your skin and keeps it there—strengthening your barrier and making your skin less reactive to stress, hormones, and inflammation. And because it’s non-comedogenic, it’s safe for daily use—even on sensitive, acne-prone skin</p><br><p>The result?</p><br><p>A routine that works with your skin, not against it.</p><p> ✨ Repaired barrier</p><p> ✨ Deep hydration</p><p> ✨ Fewer flare-ups over time</p><br><p>Instead of causing new problems, this kit helps your skin recover—and stay clear for good.</p><br></span></div></div><picture data-rid="6de09efa-8d11-47ba-9768-faf94a4ac37c" class="r-1h5oy"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/444f5aee-8343-4a3b-82c4-70293ee15186?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/444f5aee-8343-4a3b-82c4-70293ee15186?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/444f5aee-8343-4a3b-82c4-70293ee15186?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/444f5aee-8343-4a3b-82c4-70293ee15186" class="r-ncd61b" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="2f265291-6150-4e95-a972-b988afeadb9c" class="r-ff9fd1"><div data-rid="6436bfe6-8b8a-486b-9e92-5ab2aa3bf0e6" class="r-284osr"><div data-rid="16ba90f0-0a2a-4128-9c9d-691db108ec86" class="r-eqq0bp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Hydration That Won’t Clog Pores (Yes, It’s Possible)</p></span></div><div data-rid="292b9f90-212d-4c25-a81d-fc7f2f0d6a96" class="r-phwk3l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">If you’ve ever been told that moisturizers or oils will make your acne worse, you’re not alone—and you’ve also been misled. The truth is, dehydrated skin is more likely to break out. When your skin lacks moisture, it overcompensates by producing excess oil—clogging pores and triggering more hormonal flare-ups.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">The Clear Skin Kit is designed to break that cycle.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Every step in the routine delivers deep, lasting hydration while staying completely non-comedogenic—meaning it won't clog your pores or trigger new breakouts. Instead of heavy creams or harsh treatments, you get lightweight, breathable hydration that keeps your skin balanced, calm, and clear.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">You don’t have to choose between being breakout-free and well-hydrated. Blume makes sure you get both—without the fear.</span></p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="4c43e4f4-8b4b-41f5-9a5b-1af54368f73c" class="r-1yu0heu"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/c5ba92fa-cc27-4855-83ec-01ef925f6867?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/c5ba92fa-cc27-4855-83ec-01ef925f6867?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/c5ba92fa-cc27-4855-83ec-01ef925f6867?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/c5ba92fa-cc27-4855-83ec-01ef925f6867" class="r-gwlwqb" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="4f63a8ad-0845-4e9f-a808-8e3ffcb4fe02" class="r-1mfevz1"><div data-rid="b0973e13-5c64-456a-8204-a79ebeda6ad1" class="r-lfzqjl"><div data-rid="f961661f-fddd-4301-89cb-c3020a0d0de9" class="r-17iqmo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>4. Not Just Treatment—Real Prevention That Works</p></span></div><div data-rid="c07eea9f-dd9b-411d-adcd-2c5936ab0a6e" class="r-1rn0tl9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>You’ve probably cleared a breakout before—only for it to come back a week later, sometimes worse. That’s because most acne products only treat the surface symptoms, not the root cause.</p><br><p>Hormonal acne is different. It starts deep under the skin, often showing up as painful, swollen cysts that are hard to treat and slow to heal. By the time they surface, they’re already too stubborn for most spot treatments. That’s where the Clear Skin Kit comes in.</p><br><p>This 3-step routine is designed to work beneath the surface. The oil-based treatment absorbs into the skin to flatten pimples before they even come up. The gentle cleanser deeply cleans without stripping, leaving your skin soft and balanced. And the oil-free gel cream keeps your skin hydrated and your barrier protected—without clogging pores.</p><br><p>What makes the Clear Skin Kit different? Every ingredient is chosen to not only treat active breakouts but to help prevent future ones from forming. The formulas calm inflammation, reduce redness, and clear congestion—all without harsh chemicals that can irritate or dry out your skin.</p><br><p>With consistent use, your skin becomes clearer, calmer, and more resilient—so you’re no longer stuck in a cycle of breakouts, scarring, and overcorrection.</p><br><p>Clear skin shouldn’t be a short-term win. With Blume, it’s something you can maintain.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="7e22e524-0edf-4f98-b83e-8275e2053240" class="r-9mg1v4"><img src="https://www.blume.com/cdn/shop/files/Untitled_design_35_700x700_crop_center.png?v=1760562375" class="r-1kusd7o" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="f6add24e-6fd1-4918-8d5e-e19d0a4b2018" class="r-1b9kae9"><div data-rid="70453265-1588-4dc0-9806-e9a456330f94" class="r-1c9oy75"><div data-rid="d33873a7-b3a5-4832-89ab-cb0f7395e320" class="r-hmvzbv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When you’ve tried dozens of acne products, it’s only natural to feel skeptical. Will this irritate my skin? Will it disrupt my hormones? Is it even safe to use long-term? That’s exactly why we created Blume—to be the better, safer alternative.</p><p>Every product in the Clear Skin Kit is:</p><br><ul><li><p>100% Clean – Made without parabens, sulfates, phthalates, artificial dyes, or endocrine (hormone) disruptors</p></li><li><p>Vegan & Cruelty-Free – Certified by PETA and Leaping Bunny</p></li><li><p>Dermatologist-Tested – Formulated specifically for sensitive, acne-prone skin</p></li><li><p>Non-Comedogenic – Won’t clog pores or trigger breakouts</p></li><li><p>Safe for Teens, Adults, and Hormonal Skin – Free from harsh chemicals and unnecessary fillers</p></li></ul><br><p>If you're struggling with hormonal acne, the last thing you need is skincare that throws your hormones further out of balance. </p><br><p>Unfortunately, many conventional products still contain hidden endocrine disruptors—like parabens, phthalates, and artificial fragrances—that can worsen hormonal acne and make it harder to treat.</p><br><p>Blume is different. Our formulas are 100% clean, non-toxic, and plant-powered—designed to clear your skin and protect your health. Instead of harsh additives, we use gentle, science-backed ingredients that work with your body, not against it.</p><br><p>And the industry has taken notice:</p><p>🏆 Award-winning formulas featured in Allure, Teen Vogue, and Well+Good</p><p> 🌿 Recognized by the EWG (Environmental Working Group) for clean formulation standards</p><p> 💬 Trusted by thousands of customers and over 5,000 five-star reviews from people with real, sensitive skin</p><br><p>With Blume, you don’t have to choose between clean and effective. You get both—because you deserve skincare that actually works and puts your wellbeing first.</p></span></div><div data-rid="d7a88c81-906b-439b-b2da-0d313f6b7f1b" class="r-gtq1re alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>5. Clean, Vegan, and Backed by Experts—So You Can Trust What You’re Putting on Your Skin</p></span></div></div></div><picture data-rid="f3685450-6cf3-44a6-8ba1-b44bf9be30a0" class="r-gw1anq"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406" alt="Blume skincare products for acne-prone skin against a blue background." class="r-1k7eg6r" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="502b2f95-ecd2-4997-8d65-4ce640da8973" class="r-1u5ynjh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>6. Thousands Have Cleared Their Skin—and Reclaimed Their Confidence—with Blume<br></p></span></div><div data-rid="0a35f6d3-c387-4147-8325-00b564404a8c" class="r-11jgtkq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: r